      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Option 1, Oak Ridge Estates, best embodies the highly prestigious and traditionally luxury feel you are aiming for. Its focus on \"timeless elegance,\" \"historic colonial architecture,\" and \"quiet, established atmosphere\" directly appeals to a clientele seeking classic opulence and seclusion. Options 2 and 3 lean more toward trendy, vibrant, or community-focused markets, which might dilute the exclusive luxury image you want to project.",
