      "content": "I see. So you're saying the others don't really work because they're too \"vibrant\" or \"soulful\"? I was worried about that. \n\nI guess I just want to make sure we're being accurate for the client. Is it just the architecture that makes Option 1 the \"prestigious\" one, or is there something about the demographic or the \"vibe\" of those types of established neighborhoods that makes them more suitable for high-end luxury compared to the more diverse areas in Options 2 and 3?",
